_sText:
The point of scoutzknivez is to strafe around the map killing your opponents with either your scout, or your knife gaining as much speed as possible.

Scoutzknivez_Gods gives you much room to gain plenty of speed, while combining the key areas to pick the strafers from the sky.

Scoutzknivez_Gods uses the same brush structure as the original Scoutzknivez but uses different textures and layout.
    The map file includes:
  • All custom textures.
  • Nav File.
  • Txt File.
Please keep in mind the game play aspect when you assess, Thank You.
